          "Second, choose one or two bets instead of chasing everything. Look at your business and ask, where do I spend hours on work that follows a pattern? For most owners it is one of three places. Answering the same questions, producing routine content, or chasing follow ups. Pick one. Go deep on that one for a quarter. Depth in one workflow beats a shallow tour of forty tools, every time.",
